              <li><p><span><span><span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><span><span>The=
 Fidler=E2=80=99s Life Style Performance Model focuses on knowing and under=
standing a person=E2=80=99s total activity repertoire within the context re=
levant to his/her life. This model provides practitioners a complete view o=
f the client and his/her environment. It aims to bridge the gaps among the =
practice, philosophic constructs of holism, personal relevance, and quality=
 of life.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p></li>
