</a>
    </h2>
   =20

 =20
  <div>
    <div class=3D"clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--typ=
e-text-with-summary field--label-hidden">
      <ul class=3D"links field__items">
              <li><p>This model is a service delivery model that aims to pr=
ovide a framework for occupational therapists to design and evaluate servic=
es for people living with HIV. It focuses on designing and evaluating inter=
ventions that target outcomes in activity and social participation. It comp=
rises of the following components, prominent features of living with HIV, s=
ervice delivery principles, promising interventions, and person-environment=
 interactions across micro, meso, and macro levels of the environment.</p><=
/li>
        </ul>
</div>

